        "body_text": "Unicode: caf\u00e9 r\u00e9sum\u00e9",
        "body_size": 23
      }
    ]
  },
  "notes": "Charset parameter may be extracted from Content-Type. Parsers may return the full content_type value including charset, or extract charset separately. The charset field is optional."
